item.title: About Me
item.description: Welcome to my personal site! I’m a technology enthusiast that love Linux and opensource. My name is Budiman and I live in Indonesia. This is the place where I will be sharing about anything, mostly tech related. I hope this site/blog can help people learning new stuffs and have fun. This site is hosted in a Cloudflare Page with Hugo. The search box above is powered by Algolia. If you can’t find anything that means I have reached 10k requests monthly cap because I’m cheap and use the Free Plan.
